data.description: Affordable, 1.28 acre country property located in the Anna Local School District.  This two story farmhouse features a spacious kitchen with granite countertops, a large island and stainless steel kitchen appliances.  The dining room and living room are equally spacious and the pellet stove in the dining room will stay.  Finishing out the first floor is the bathroom, a bedroom and the utility room.  Upstairs you will find three large bedrooms.  The propane forced air furnace was installed in 2021.  Outside you will find a patio, shed, and a 26 x 36 pole building.  Make your appointment to see this country property today!!
